# Secrets — defense in depth. The app stores keys in
# %APPDATA%\com.onetruedutchie.app\keys.json, never inside the repo.
# These patterns block accidental commits if someone copies that file
# or generates one in the project dir.
keys.json
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
**/secrets/
*.secret
